{
  "chapter": 40,
  "chapter_summary": "本章中，谢晓峰面对简传学的背叛，选择宽容放其离去。欧阳云鹤、厉真真等七大剑派首徒表明立场——他们不惜一切手段对抗天尊慕容秋荻，维护江湖正义。谢晓峰未杀他们，因理解江湖人身不由己的悲哀。简传学再次找到谢晓峰，坦白自己是天尊的人，但因医者仁心未加害谢晓峰，并揭露田在龙也是天尊棋子。谢晓峰点破厉真真实为天尊暗探，却故意放过她，因其能制衡慕容秋荻。简传学最后告知有人能救谢晓峰之伤，但那人已无法找到。全章展现谢晓峰复杂深沉的性格——既冷酷无情又宽大仁慈，既多情又无情，在生死边缘仍保持超然的洞察力。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的，是我说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是天尊的人，田在龙也是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我告诉田在龙的，所以他们才会知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看错了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我把你当做朋友，就是看错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不怪你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的不怪我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不怪你，只因为你本来并不认得我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的，我本来不认得你，一点都不认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢晓峰果然不愧是谢晓峰。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果我是你，绝不会放他走的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也不是欧阳云鹤、梅长华、秦独秀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为你不是，所以你才不了解我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你才会觉得我们不该杀了黎平子和田在龙的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们早已决定了，只要能达到目的，不择任何手段。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们的目的只有八个字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对抗天尊，维护正义。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许我们用的手段不对，我们想做的事却绝对没有什么不对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_chang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "梅长华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你若认为我们杀错了人，不妨就用这柄剑来杀了我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们非但绝不还手，而且死无怨恨！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是个女人，女人都比较怕死，可是我也死而无怨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhen_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "厉真真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们都是人，都是江湖人，所以你应该知道我们为什么要这样做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_yun_he",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳云鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们选她来作盟主，因为我们觉得只有她才能对付天尊慕容秋荻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你不愿再见我，可是我非来不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我心里有些话，不管你愿不愿意听，我都非说出来不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你一定要说，我就听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的确是天尊的人，因为我无法拒绝他们，因为我还不想死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明白，连田在龙那样的人都不能拒绝他们，何况你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我跟他不同，他学的是剑，我学的是医，医道是济世救人的，将人的性命看得比什么都重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我投入天尊只不过才几个月，学医却已有二十年，对人命的这种看法，早已在我心里根深蒂固。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以不管天尊要我怎么做，我都绝不会将人命当儿戏，只要是我的病人，我一定会全心全力去为他医治，不管他是什么人都一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就连你都一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜我的伤确实已无救了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要我觉得还有一分希望，我都绝不会放手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你已尽了力，我并没有怪你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "田在龙的确也是天尊的人，他们本来想要我安排，让他杀了你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种事也能安排？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别人不能，我能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么安排？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要我在你伤口上再加一点腐骨的药，你遇见田在龙时，就会连还击之力都没有了，只要我给他一点暗示，他就出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论谁能击败谢家的三少爷，都必将震动江湖，名重天下，何况他们之间还有赌约。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁杀了谢晓峰，谁就是泰山之会的盟主？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "田在龙若能在七大剑派的首徒面前杀了我，厉真真也只有将盟主的宝座让给他，那么七大剑派的联盟，也就变成了天尊的囊中物。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜你并没有这么样做。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不能这么样做，我做不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为医道的仁心，已经在你心里生了根。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我只有一点还想不通。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "厉真真他们怎么会知道我最多只能再活三天的？这件事本该只有天尊的人知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道厉真真也是天尊的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的不知道她也是天尊的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实你应该想得到的，高手着棋，每个子后面，都一定埋伏着更厉害的杀手，慕容秋荻对田在龙这个人本就没把握，在这局棋中，她真正的杀着本就是厉真真。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你早已想到了这一着？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我并不太笨。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你当然已经杀了她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么放过了她？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为只有她才能对付慕容秋荻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是她……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在她虽然还是天尊的人，可是她绝不会久居在慕容秋荻之下，泰山之会正是她最好的机会，只要她一登上盟主的宝座，就一定会利用她的权力，全力对付天尊。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我了解她这种人，她绝不会放过这种机会的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕容秋荻一直在利用她，却不知道她也一直在利用慕容秋荻，她投入天尊，也许就是为了要利用天尊的力量，踏上这一步。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕容秋荻下的这一着棋，就像是养条毒蛇，毒蛇虽然能制人于死，可是随时都可能回过头去反噬一口的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一口也能致命？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她能够让慕容秋荻信任她，当然也能查出天尊的命脉在哪里，这一口若是咬在天尊的命脉上，当然咬得不轻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是百足之虫，死而不僵，她若想一口致命，只怕还不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我们正好以毒攻毒，让他们互相残杀，等到他们精疲力竭的时候，别的人就可以取而代之了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别的人是什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江湖中每一代都有英雄兴起，会是什么人？谁也不知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是江湖人的命运，生活在江湖中，就像是风中的落叶，水中的浮萍，往往都是身不由主的，我们只要知道，七派联盟和天尊都必败无疑，也就足够了，又何必问得太多。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这次来，本来还有件事想告诉你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽然不能治你的伤，你的伤却并不是绝对无救。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有谁能救我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他也是个很奇怪的人，也像你一样，变化无常，捉摸不定，有时候甚至也像你一样冷酷无情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管这个人是谁，现在你都已永远找不到他了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可以杀了我，可是你就算杀了我，我也不会说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为现在我才真正了解你是个什么样的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你远比任何人想像中的都无情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你连自己的生死都不放在心上，当然更不会看重别人的生命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要你认为必要时，你随时都可以牺牲别人的，不管那个人是谁都一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我活着还不如死了的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我并不想看着你死，我不说，只因为我一定要保护那个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    }
